name: Fractured
description: Every moment you live is a part of you. Every wound, every crack defines you. Your whole being can explode, but that doesn't mean you can't be whole again. - A special OBJKT, created by coincidence on the day HEN died, and which resonates with that particular moment. What matters isn't a website, but the strong community we built. Long live to HEN! (10s loop + sound - 1080x1080 - 60fps - created by @ufunk_parse)
